<exercise>
	<title>Equality of matrices</title>
	<p> What conditions must be checked to verify that two matrices are equal? </p>
</exercise>

<exercise>
	<title>Matrix operations</title>
	<p>
		For each, describe in one sentence how to carry out the operation.
		<ol>
			<li> matrix addition       </li>
			<li> matrix subtraction    </li>
			<li> scalar multiplication </li>
			<li> transpose             </li>
		</ol>
	</p>
</exercise>

